[quote name='_Augustus_']Maybe make the green a little more olive?<br>
<br>
Also, the engine arrangement on the Nova mount isn&#39;t quite right. It should be a + shape.[/QUOTE]<br>
<br>
psst, hey, kid, over here... don&#39;t let Shadowmage know I got you this, alright?<br>
<br>
[CODE]SSTU_ENGINELAYOUT{<br>
