}<br>
}<br>
+PART[SSTU_ShipCore_ENG-F1]:NEEDS[SSTU]:FINAL<br>
{<br>
@name = SSTU_ShipCore_ENG-F1_Nova_C-8<br>
@title = SSTU - SC-ENG-F1 Nova C-8<br>
@mass *= 8<br>
@MODULE[SSTUEngineCluster]<br>
{<br>
@layoutName = Nova_C-8<br>
//@mountSpacing = 3.125<br>
!MOUNT,*{}<br>
}<br>
@MODULE[ModuleEngines*]<br>
{<br>
@maxThrust *= 8<br>
}<br>
@MODULE[ModuleEngineConfigs]<br>
{<br>
@CONFIG,*<br>
{<br>
@minThrust *= 8<br>
@maxThrust *= 8<br>
}<br>
}<br>
}[/CODE]<br>
<br>
and no, he didn&#39;t make this config, I made it in a matter of like 10 to 15 minutes including testing these<br>
